== Manual Verification Steps ==
1. Build & run the app
2. Confirm Configuration window launches with 1/4 SLOTS ACTIVE
3. Click '+ SLOT' button — confirm AddSlotSheet modal appears
4. Enter name, select icon, select schedule (Daily/Weekly/Specific Days)
5. Click 'ADD SLOT' — confirm habit appears in list, counter updates
6. Add habits to 4/4 — confirm '+ SLOT' button disappears
7. Select 'Specific Days' — confirm day toggle buttons appear with clear selected state
8. Try saving with empty name — confirm ADD SLOT button is disabled
9. Right-click habit row — confirm Delete context menu appears
10. Delete a habit — confirm removal and counter update
11. Click habit row — confirm Habit Streak placeholder sheet opens

== User Feedback ==
